  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.3,
      "size": 20736,
      "text": "定积分能求出曲线下方的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "那么一张起伏的曲面下方，又该怎样求出它包住的体积呢？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.2,
      "size": 19152,
      "text": "这正是二重积分要回答的问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "在矩形区域上，我们把曲面下方的立体切成许许多多细长的小柱子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "每根柱子的体积，等于底面小块的面积乘以那里的函数高度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 43920,
      "text": "把所有柱子的体积加起来，就得到二重积分，写作对 f 关于面积元 dA 的积分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "itr-1",
      "filename": "iterate-itr-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/iterate-itr-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.6,
      "size": 25632,
      "text": "实际计算时，我们把它拆成两次一维积分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "itr-2",
      "filename": "iterate-itr-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/iterate-itr-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "先固定 y，沿 x 方向积一刀，得到一个截面的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "itr-3",
      "filename": "iterate-itr-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/iterate-itr-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "再让这个面积沿 y 方向累加起来，体积就求出来了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "approx",
      "line_id": "apx-1",
      "filename": "approx-apx-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/approx-apx-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "在屏幕上，我们把区域划成 n 乘 n 的网格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "approx",
      "line_id": "apx-2",
      "filename": "approx-apx-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/approx-apx-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "取每个小格的中心点算出高度，颜色越暖表示柱子越高。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "approx",
      "line_id": "apx-3",
      "filename": "approx-apx-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/approx-apx-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "把每根柱子的体积相加，就是逼近真实体积的黎曼和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "试着调大网格密度，看近似的体积如何一步步逼近真值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "再换不同的函数和区域，观察热力图和体积怎样随之改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "二重积分把曲面下方的体积，化成无数小柱子的累加。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.52,
      "size": 24336,
      "text": "累次积分让我们先横后纵地一步步算出它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "网格越密，逼近越准，这就是重积分的思想，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
